Package: securecontext
Title: Memory, Knowledge Persistence, and Context Management for Large
    Language Model Agents
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ian", "Flores Siaca", , "iflores.siaca@hey.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Provides memory, knowledge persistence, Retrieval-Augmented
    Generation (RAG) retrieval, and token-aware context window management
    for Large Language Model (LLM) agents. Includes document chunking,
    Term Frequency-Inverse Document Frequency (TF-IDF) embeddings, vector
    search, persistent key-value knowledge stores, and priority-based
    context assembly.
